[
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 5.1,
    "text": "Don't you want you [sic] know our names?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.42,
    "endTime": 6.88,
    "text": "Can't imagine how it would matter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.58,
    "endTime": 9.56,
    "text": "Come quickly! Far too much to see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.8,
    "endTime": 17.64,
    "text": "Just drop your coats anywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.96,
    "endTime": 26.560000000000002,
    "text": "Mr. Wonka? Sure is toasty in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.96,
    "endTime": 27.46,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.76,
    "endTime": 32.36,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, I have to keep it warm in here because my workers are used to an extremely hot climate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.74,
    "endTime": 34.32,
    "text": "They just can't stand the cold."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.64,
    "endTime": 35.56,
    "text": "Who are the workers?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.12,
    "endTime": 38.18,
    "text": "All in good time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.44,
    "endTime": 39.059,
    "text": "Now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.98,
    "endTime": 42.48,
    "text": "*gasp*"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 45.26,
    "text": "Mr. Wonka, I'm Violet Beauregarde."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.42,
    "endTime": 46.92,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.06,
    "endTime": 48.900000000000006,
    "text": "I don't care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.26,
    "endTime": 52.699,
    "text": "Well, you should care because I'm the girl who's gonna win the special prize at the end."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.84,
    "endTime": 55.56,
    "text": "Well, you do seem confident and confidence is key."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.94,
    "endTime": 61.48,
    "text": "I'm Veruca Salt. It's very nice to meet you, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.5,
    "endTime": 66.22,
    "text": "I always thought a verruca was a type of wart you got on the bottom of you foot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.46,
    "endTime": 66.96,
    "text": "*giggle*"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.04,
    "endTime": 71.96000000000001,
    "text": "I'm Augustus Gloop. I love your chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.4,
    "endTime": 78.16000000000001,
    "text": "I can see that. So do I. I never expected to have so much in common."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.24,
    "endTime": 83.92,
    "text": "You."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.76,
    "endTime": 85.82000000000001,
    "text": "You're Mike Teavee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.64,
    "endTime": 88.56,
    "text": "You're the little devil who cracked the system."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.0,
    "endTime": 93.72,
    "text": "And you. Well, you're just lucky to be here, aren't you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.06,
    "endTime": 97.36,
    "text": "And the rest of you must be their p-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.16,
    "endTime": 106.74,
    "text": "Parents."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.34,
    "endTime": 109.8,
    "text": "Yeah. Moms and dads."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.3,
    "endTime": 112.899,
    "text": "Dad?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.88,
    "endTime": 116.44,
    "text": "Papa?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.34,
    "endTime": 126.5,
    "text": "Okay then. Let's move along."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.7,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "Is it just me or does Wonka seem a few quarters short of a buck?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.88,
    "endTime": 141.46,
    "text": "I'm sorry, I don't speak American."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.68,
    "endTime": 145.12,
    "text": "Would you like some chocolate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.3,
    "endTime": 145.8,
    "text": "Sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.04,
    "endTime": 147.48,
    "text": "Then you should have brought some."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.78,
    "endTime": 153.1,
    "text": "Let's be friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.36,
    "endTime": 154.36,
    "text": "Best friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.6,
    "endTime": 167.85899999999998,
    "text": "An important room, this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.32,
    "endTime": 170.64,
    "text": "After all, it is a chocolate factory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.72,
    "endTime": 172.28,
    "text": "Then why is the door so small?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.26,
    "endTime": 175.82,
    "text": "That's to keep all the great big chocolaty flavor inside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.9,
    "endTime": 176.44,
    "text": "*giggle*"
  }
]